Requirements

Create Loan API

POST /api/v1/loans 

Request Body:
{
  "customerId": "CUST123",
  "amount": 50000,
  "tenureMonths": 24
}


Business Rules:
amount must be > 0
tenureMonths must be between 6 and 60
A customer cannot have more than ONE active loan (CREATED or APPROVED)
Loan status initially = CREATED
Loan ID auto-generated


Response:
{
  "loanId": 1,
  "status": "CREATED"
}

LoansController
/api/v1/

RequestMapping /api/v1/loans

Request Body -> CreateLoanRequestDTO 

customerId
amount
tenureMonths

Response -> CreateLoanResponseDTO

loanId
status

LoanRepository

    createLoan()

LoanEntity

customerId
amount
tenureMonths
loanId
status



